-300 rounded-xl pl-2.5 py-[var(--msg-bubble-py,0.625rem)] break-words text-text-100 transition-all max-w-[75ch] flex-col !px-[var(--msg-bubble-px,1rem)] max-w-[85%]" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="flex flex-row gap-2 relative"><div class="flex-1"><div data-testid="user-message" class="font-large !font-user-message py-0.5 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 relative [&amp;_ul]:!space-y-0 [&amp;_ol]:!space-y-0 [&amp;_ul]:pl-8 [&amp;_ol]:pl-8" style="max-height: none; overflow: hidden; position: relative;"><p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Q: Do you have Tableau or Power BI installed and want to build this yourself with my guidance, or would you like me to build the actual charts/dashboard for you (I can create these directly using Python or an interactive HTML dashboard)?
