Validated chart accuracy and orchestrated workflow progression</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Now that's the real story — x-axis is now a proper average discount (0.00 to 0.35), and the trend line slopes downward as expected: higher average discount correlates with lower profit. You can also see it visually in the dots — the two clear loss-makers (around -10K and -20K) sit at 0.20-0.30 average discount, while the highest-profit dots cluster down near 0.10-0.15 discount. That's your causal explanation for the Tables/Bookcases losses from Chart 2.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Rename this sheet — double-click "Sheet 3" at the bottom and call it "Discount Impact on Profit."</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Now let's build the last chart, <strong>Sales by State</strong> (the map), then move to assembling everything into the dashboard.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Right-click a sheet tab → New Worksheet. Then:<br>
Double-click <strong>State</strong> in the Data pane on the left — Tableau will automatically build a map for you.<br>
Drag <strong>Sales</strong> onto <strong>Color</strong> (in the Marks card) — this shades each state by sales volume.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Rename that sheet "Sales by State" once it's built, then send a screenshot and we'll move to Step 8: assembling the Dashboard.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-message-action-bar="" class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 pointer-coarse:opacity-100 transition"><div class="text-text-300"><div role="toolbar" aria-label="Message actions" class="text-text-300 flex select-none items-stretch justify-between"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none cursor-[var(--cds-cursor-interactive)] aria-disabled:cursor-default data-[disabled]:cursor-default border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0 !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Copy" data-testid="action-bar-copy" id="base-ui-_r_10g_" tabindex="0"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; a