 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">That fixed it perfectly — full color-coded US map, and you can already read the story: <strong>California, Texas, and New York are your darkest (highest-sales) states</strong>, clearly standing out from the lighter-shaded majority. That's a clean closing insight for your storyboard ("sales are concentrated in a few coastal/major states").</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">That's all four core charts done:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Sales &amp; Profit Trend (line)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Profitability by Sub-Category (bar, with annotation)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Discount Impact on Profit (scatter + trend line)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Sales by State (map)</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Now for <strong>Step 8 — building the Dashboard.</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Click the small <strong>"New Dashboard"</strong> icon next to your sheet tabs at the bottom (same plus-style icon area, but there's a separate dashboard icon — or go to the top menu: <strong>Dashboard → New Dashboard</strong>).</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Once on the blank dashboard canvas:<br>
On the left side, you'll see a list of your sheets (Sales &amp; Profit Trend, Profitability by Sub-Category, Discount Impact on Profit, Sales by State). Drag each one onto the canvas, one at a time — Tableau will auto-tile them into a grid.<br>
Resize by dragging the edges/borders between charts so all four are clearly visible and not too squished.<br>
From the <strong>Objects</strong> list (usually below the sheet list on the left), drag a <strong>Text</strong> object to the very top of the dashboard. Click into it and type a headline insight, e.g.: <em>"Furniture discounting is eroding profit — Tables and Bookcases lose money despite strong overall sales growth."</em></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Send a screenshot once you've got all four sheets on the dashboard, even if the layout looks rough — we'll clean it up together.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-message-action-bar="" class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 pointer-coarse:opacity-100 transition"><div class="text-text-300"><div role="toolbar" aria-label="Message actions" class="text-text-300 flex select-none items-stretch justify-between"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none cursor-[var(--cds-cursor-interactive)] aria-disabled:cursor-default data-[disabled]:cursor-default border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0 !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Copy" data-testid="action-bar-copy" id="base-ui-_r_134_" tabindex="0"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-