lative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div data-find-omitted="" class="contents"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-[var(--msg-pill-py,0.375rem)]"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="relative h-5 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 overflow-hidden transition-[width,margin-right] duration-150 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.25,0.9,0.3,1)] w-0 -mr-2"><div class="pt-1"><div aria-hidden="true"><div class="!w-5 !text-brand-200 w-8 text-accent-brand inline-block select-none" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-full fill-current"><path d="m19.6 66.5 19.7-11 .3-1-.3-.5h-1l-3.3-.2-11.2-.3L14 53l-9.5-.5-2.4-.5L0 49l.2-1.5 2-1.3 2.9.2 6.3.5 9.5.6 6.9.4L38 49.1h1.6l.2-.7-.5-.4-.4-.4L29 41l-10.6-7-5.6-4.1-3-2-1.5-2-.6-4.2 2.7-3 3.7.3.9.2 3.7 2.9 8 6.1L37 36l1.5 1.2.6-.4.1-.3-.7-1.1L33 25l-6-10.4-2.7-4.3-.7-2.6c-.3-1-.4-2-.4-3l3-4.2L28 0l4.2.6L33.8 2l2.6 6 4.1 9.3L47 29.9l2 3.8 1 3.4.3 1h.7v-.5l.5-7.2 1-8.7 1-11.2.3-3.2 1.6-3.8 3-2L61 2.6l2 2.9-.3 1.8-1.1 7.7L59 27.1l-1.5 8.2h.9l1-1.1 4.1-5.4 6.9-8.6 3-3.5L77 13l2.3-1.8h4.3l3.1 4.7-1.4 4.9-4.4 5.6-3.7 4.7-5.3 7.1-3.2 5.7.3.4h.7l12-2.6 6.4-1.1 7.6-1.3 3.5 1.6.4 1.6-1.4 3.4-8.2 2-9.6 2-14.3 3.3-.2.1.2.3 6.4.6 2.8.2h6.8l12.6 1 3.3 2 1.9 2.7-.3 2-5.1 2.6-6.8-1.6-16-3.8-5.4-1.3h-.8v.4l4.6 4.5 8.3 7.5L89 80.1l.5 2.4-1.3 2-1.4-.2-9.2-7-3.6-3-8-6.8h-.5v.7l1.8 2.7 9.8 14.7.5 4.5-.7 1.4-2.6 1-2.7-.6-5.8-8-6-9-4.7-8.2-.5.4-2.9 30.2-1.3 1.5-3 1.2-2.5-2-1.4-3 1.4-6.2 1.6-8 1.3-6.4 1.2-7.9.7-2.6v-.2H49L43 72l-9 12.3-7.2 7.6-1.7.7-3-1.5.3-2.8L24 86l10-12.8 6-7.9 4-4.6-.1-.5h-.3L17.2 77.4l-4.7.6-2-2 .2-3 1-1 8-5.5Z"></path></svg></div></div></div></div><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate font-base">Formulated clear instructions for dashboard integration</span><span class="inline-flex -rotate-90 shrink-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-200 group-hover/status:opacity-100 group-focus-visible/status:opacity-100"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Formulated clear instructions for dashboard integration</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Here's the step-by-step for that:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>1. Create the Story sheet.</strong> Right-click any sheet tab at the bottom (next to "Dashboard 1") and choose <strong>New Story</strong> — or go to the top menu: <strong>Story → New Story</strong>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>2. Find your dashboard in the left panel.</strong> Once you're on the blank Story canvas, you'll see a "Story" panel on the left side, similar to the Dashboard panel — it lists all your sheets AND dashboards together. Scroll down if needed; "Dashboard 1" should appear in that list, usually with a small dashboard-style icon next to it (different from the individual sheet icons).</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>3. Drag it onto the canvas.</strong> Click and hold on "Dashboard 1" in that left list, then drag it onto the large blank area in the center that says something like "Drag a sheet here to begin your story." Release once you're hovering over that drop zone.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>4. Add the caption.</strong> At the top of the canvas, there's a text box that says something like "Add a caption" — click it and type your first story-point caption, e.g. "Overview: Where we make and lose money."</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>5. Add more story points (optional, for the full storyboard).</strong> Click the <strong>"Duplicate"</strong> button that appears just above the canvas (it looks like two overlapping rectangles, near the top-left of the story toolbar). This creates a second story point with the same dashboard — change its caption to something like "Where we're losing money," and optionally click on a specific chart within that duplicated point to highlight it (Tableau will remember that selection as part of that story point). Repeat for 2-3 more points to walk through your narrative.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Send a screenshot once the dashboard is sitting on the story canvas and I'll help with the captions or layout from there.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-message-action-bar="" class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 pointer-coarse:opacity-100 transition"><div class="text-text-300"><div role="toolbar" aria-label="Message actions" class="text-text-300 flex select-none items-stretch justify-between"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none cursor-[var(--cds-cursor-interactive)] aria-disabled:cursor-default data-[disabled]:cursor-default border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0 !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Copy" data-testid="action-bar-copy" id="base-ui-_r_1b4_" tabindex="0"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; align-