s from your click — that's the focus interaction working as intended, drawing the eye to where you clicked. This is a complete storyboard.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">You're done with the build. Last step: <strong>File → Export → PDF</strong> (top menu, not the panel on the left). Tableau will ask whether to export the active sheet/story or the entire workbook — choose <strong>active sheet</strong> so it exports just this Story with all 4 points, which becomes your final "Visual report" deliverable.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">If your assignment wants screenshots instead of a PDF, you can also just click through each of the 4 captions and take a screenshot of each, then drop them into a doc or slide deck in order.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Either way, you've hit every part of the brief: right charts for the data, minimal clutter, a clear takeaway on the sub-category chart, context via captions and trend lines, business-insight framing throughout, and now a proper sequential storyboard. Nice work pushing through the annotation and map issues.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-message-action-bar="" class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 pointer-coarse:opacity-100 transition"><div class="text-text-300"><div role="toolbar" aria-label="Message actions" class="text-text-300 flex select-none items-stretch justify-between"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none cursor-[var(--cds-cursor-interactive)] aria-disabled:cursor-default data-[disabled]:cursor-default border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0 !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Copy" data-testid="action-bar-copy" id="base-ui-_r_1cg_" tabindex="0"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable);