          ease-[cubic-bezier(0.165,0.85,0.45,1)] h-8 w-8 rounded-md backdrop-blur-md _fill_10ocf_9 _ghost_10ocf_96" type="button" aria-label="Copy to clipboard" data-state="closed"><div class="relative"><div class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M12.5 3A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 14 4.5V6h1.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 17 7.5v8a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 6 15.5V14H4.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 12.5v-8A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 3zm1.5 9.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5H7v1.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5H14zM4.5 4a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h8a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-8a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5z"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M15.188 5.11a.5.5 0 0 1 .752.626l-.056.084-7.5 9a.5.5 0 0 1-.738.033l-3.5-3.5-.064-.078a.501.501 0 0 1 .693-.693l.078.064 3.113 3.113 7.15-8.58z"></path></svg></div></div></div></button></div></div><div class="text-text-500 font-small p-3.5 pb-0">markdown</div><div class="overflow-x-auto"><pre class="code-block__code !my-0 !rounded-lg !text-sm !leading-relaxed p-3.5" style="color: rgb(20, 24, 31); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono);"><code class="language-markdown" style="color: rgb(20, 24, 31); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre;"><span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">#</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Furniture Discounting Erodes Profit</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Data Visualization &amp; Storytelling — Superstore Sales Analysis</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Objective</span><span>
</span></span><span>Analyze Superstore sales data to uncover business insights around profitability, discounting, and regional performance, and present them as a clear visual story.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Tools</span><span>
</span></span><span>Tableau Public
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Dataset</span><span>
</span></span><span>Sample Superstore dataset — 9,994 orders across Category, Sub-Category, Region, Sales, Profit, Discount, and Order Date.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Story</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Overview: Where we're making and losing money</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(20, 24, 31);">!</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">[</span><span class="token token content" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">Overview</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">](</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">overview.png</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">)</span><span>
</span></span><span>Sales and profit both trended upward from 2014 to 2017, with sales growing faster than profit.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Furniture is the problem</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(20, 24, 31);">!</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">[</span><span class="token token content" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">Sub-category profitability</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">](</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">subcategory.png</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">)</span><span>
</span></span><span>Tables and Bookcases are the only loss-making sub-categories — Tables alone lost $17,725, likely due to high shipping costs relative to price.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Why: higher discounts erode profit</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(20, 24, 31);">!</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">[</span><span class="token token content" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">Discount impact</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">](</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">discount.png</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">)</span><span>
</span></span><span>Higher average discount rates correlate with lower profit across sub-categories.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Where sales concentrate</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(20, 24, 31);">!</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">[</span><span class="token token content" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">Sales by state</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">](</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">map.png</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128);">)</span><span>
</span></span><span>California, Texas, and New York drive a disproportionate share of total revenue.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Recommendation</span><span>
</span></span><span>Reduce discounting on Tables and Bookcases, or re-evaluate shipping and pricing structure for those sub-categories to restore profitability.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(43, 48, 59); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(184, 10, 24); font-weight: bold;"> Interactive workbook</span><span>
</span></span><span>The full interactive Tableau workbook is included in this repo for exploration.</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Commit that, and your repo homepage will show your title, all 4 charts, and the insights laid out as a real report. Send a screenshot once you've uploaded the images and updated the README.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-message-action-bar="" class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 pointer-coarse:opacity-100 transition"><div class="text-text-300"><div role="toolbar" aria-label="Message actions" class="text-text-300 flex select-none items-stretch justify-between"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none cursor-[var(--cds-cursor-interactive)] aria-disabled:cursor-default data-[disabled]:cursor-default border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0 !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Copy" data-testid="action-bar-copy" id="base-ui-_r_1i3_" tabindex="0"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: no