-body break-words whitespace-normal">All 4 screenshots are now collected. Here's a summary of what you have:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>overview.png</strong> — the first one you sent (Overview tab)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>subcategory.png</strong> — story point 2 (Furniture is the problem tab)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>discount.png</strong> — Image 1 just sent (Why: higher discounts tab)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>map.png</strong> — Image 2 just sent (Where sales concentrate tab)</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Now do this:</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>1. Rename all 4 files</strong> on your computer to exactly those names above before uploading — <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">overview.png</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">subcategory.png</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">discount.png</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">map.png</code>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>2. Go to your GitHub repo</strong> → click <strong>Add file → Upload files</strong> → drag all 4 renamed screenshots in → click <strong>Commit changes</strong>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>3. Edit your README.</strong> Click on <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">README.md</code> in your repo → click the pencil/edit icon → replace everything with the README I gave you earlier (the one with the 4 image references) → click <strong>Commit changes</strong>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Once committed, your repo's main page will automatically display all 4 screenshots in order with your captions and insights, looking like a proper visual report. That's your complete deliverable — just share the GitHub link.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Well done for seeing this all the way through, from connecting the data in Tableau to a finished storyboard on GitHub!</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-message-action-bar="" class="flex justify-start"><div class="text-text-300"><div role="toolbar" aria-label="Message actions" class="text-text-300 flex select-none items-stretch justify-between"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none cursor-[var(--cds-cursor-interactive)] aria-disabled:cursor-default data-[disabled]:cursor-default border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0 !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Copy" data-testid="action-bar-copy" id="base-ui-_r_1sb_" tabindex="0"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; user-select: none; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 4